TextEng: What's your name?
Can I ask you some questions?
I need some directions.
Uh, what your name?
Me have questions, okay?
Me lost. This be big place.
Text: 나 길 잃었어. 여기 진짜 커.

TextEng: Goodbye.
Hi, I'm <FirstName>.
You may call me <FullName>.
Sorry, I generally don't give out my name.
Forget it, I'm not telling you who I am.
Text: 됐어, 내가 누군지 안 알려줄 거야.

TextEng: Uh, me is <FirstName>, yuh?
Me called <FullName>, yuh? Me happy to meet you.
Sorry, me no like saying name. Too many letters.
Text: 미안, 나 이름 말하기 싫어. 글자 너무 많아.

TextEng: Hmph. Me no tell you nothing.
What kind of trouble?
What troubles you tell of?
Where can I find these wolves?
Text: 그 늑대들은 어디서 찾을 수 있어?

TextEng: That doesn't seem like a whole lot of money.
Text: 돈이 그리 많은 것 같진 않은데.

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> Maybe if I you gave a bit of an advance...
What kind of threat do these wolves pose?
Text: 그 늑대들이 어떤 위협이 되는 거지?

TextEng: Sure, that sounds like something I could do.
Text: 알았어, 내가 할 수 있을 것 같아.

TextEng: Sorry, it doesn't sound like high adventure...
Text: 미안, 별로 대단한 모험 같진 않은데...

TextEng: Uh, how me find dese wolfies?
Text: 어, 나 그 늑대들 어떻게 찾아?

TextEng: Uh, that don't sound like heap load of money....
Text: 어, 그거 돈 많은 것 같지 않아...

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> Maybe you give me gold first, yuh?
There be other dangers?
Yuh, me do it.
Uh, me rather not do that...
Text: 어, 나 그거 안 하고 싶어...

TextEng: What was it that you had wanted me to do?
Actually, I have Silverback's head right here.
Text: 사실, 은빛등의 머리를 여기 갖고 있어.

TextEng: I've changed my mind. I'll look into your troubles.
Text: 마음이 바뀌었어. 그 문제를 해결해 줄게.

TextEng: Sorry, it still doesn't sound like my game.
Text: 미안, 여전히 내 취향은 아닌 것 같아.

TextEng: Uh, what you want again?
Me have wolfie head right here.
Me want to help with trouble now, okay?
Text: 나 이제 문제 도와주고 싶어, 알았지?

TextEng: Me still no interested in yer troubles.
Text: 나 아직도 네 문제 관심 없어.

TextEng: That'll do, Pete. That'll do.
<StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> I think I've earned a higher reward than that.
Text: <StartCheck>[설득]</Start> 그것보다 더 높은 보상을 받을 자격이 있다고 생각해.

TextEng: More money, fool, or I'll have your head, too!
Text: 돈 더 내놔, 바보야, 아니면 네 머리도 가져갈 거야!

TextEng: Yuh, that be all right.
<StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> Me have hard time. You give more money, yuh?
Text: <StartCheck>[설득]</Start> 나 힘들었어. 돈 더 줘, 응?

TextEng: You give more gold or me start taking more heads!
Text: 금화 더 줘 아니면 나 머리 더 가져갈 거야!

TextEng: No reward necessary. The joy of the hunt was reward enough.
Text: 보상은 필요 없어. 사냥의 즐거움만으로 충분해.

TextEng: Me no need money. Me have enough fun chasing wolfies.
Text: 나 돈 필요 없어. 늑대 쫓는 거 재밌었어.

TextEng: Where do I find these wolves again?
I'll be back after I find the wolf.
No. It still seems like too much trouble.
Where me find these wolfies?
Me find you big bad wolf soon, yuh?
Text: 나 곧 큰 나쁜 늑대 찾아올게, 응?

TextEng: No. That trouble be too much... trouble.
Mind if I ask you a few more questions?
Me ask questions, yuh?
I'd like to ask you a few questions.
Me ask you questions, yuh?
Well I didn't kill Silverback but I did speak with her...
Well... Me no kill wolfie but me speak with her, yuh?
Text: 음... 나 늑대 안 죽였어 근데 얘기했어, 응?

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> She gave me her word. She'll stick to it.
<StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> She give me her word, yuh? She stick to it.
Fine, I'll get you her head...
*Sigh* Okay, me get you her head, then.
Text: (한숨) 알았어, 나 그녀 머리 가져다 줄게.

TextEng: Find someone else, then, because I'm not killing her...
Text: 그럼 다른 사람 찾아, 난 그녀를 죽이지 않을 거니까...

TextEng: Find some other <lad/lass>. Me not kill her, okay?
Text: 다른 사람 찾아. 나 그녀 안 죽여, 알았지?

TextEng: Regardless, I have a few questions.
Okay, but me still have questions, yuh?
Text: 알았어, 근데 나 아직 질문 있어, 응?

TextEng: More money, fool, or I'll take your head instead of the wolf's!
Text: 돈 더 내놔, 바보야, 아니면 늑대 대신 네 머리를 가져갈 거야!

TextEng: No reward necessary. That I helped both you and Silverback is enough for me.
Text: 보상은 필요 없어. 너와 은빛등 둘 다 도운 것만으로 충분해.

TextEng: You give more gold or me take your head instead!
Text: 금화 더 줘 아니면 네 머리 가져갈 거야!

TextEng: Me no need money. Me just glad you an' Silverback be friends now.
Text: 나 돈 필요 없어. 나 그냥 너랑 은빛등이 친구 된 거 기뻐.

TextEng: I have some questions about your troubles.
Text: 네 문제에 대해 몇 가지 물어볼 게 있어.

TextEng: Me have questions 'bout the troubles you having.
Text: 나 네가 겪는 문제에 대해 질문 있어.

TextEng: All right, that's enough information to make a decision on.
You talk enough, yuh? Me decide now.
Text: 말 충분히 했어, 응? 나 이제 결정할게.

TextEng: How many cattle do you have?
Uh, how many moo-cows you got?
